profile:
Get More From Your Outdoors!

We are a full-service interlocking stone company. Driveway, walkways, patio, pool decks armor stone, flagstone and more...
Let us help you add curb appeal and living space to your home.

We only use high quality building materials which will ensure our customers that their job will remain strong and look great for many years to come. 

Services Provided
Driveway Repair, Excavating,Land Leveling & Grading, Patio Construction, Retaining Wall Construction, Stone Installation, flagstone, landscapin, custom work, flagstone porches & much more. 

Areas we service: 
Vaughan, Markham, King City, Nobleton, Kleinburg, Aurora, New Market, East & West Gwillimbury, Whitchurch-Stouffville, Oakville, Georgina
warranty_terms: Up to 2 years, dependent on project

profile:
Ashmore Landscaping Inc. has been established with the purpose of providing the highest quality, clean and professional contracting services to Simcoe County and surrounding areas. 

We offer a satisfaction guarantee policy and respond to all customers within 24 hours!

​

Our mission is to provide our community with flexibility to enjoy their space stress free! We understand that our neighbors work hard and want to enjoy some relaxing down time when they get home and may not want to chore or maintain their property. This is where we come in by providing seasonal and annual maintenance options to suit your needs and eliminate the stress associated with maintaining your property.

Fencing

Residential, Ornamental, Commercial and Agricultural Fencing

profile:
Vann Brothers Landscaping Inc., has earned a reputation in Central Ontario as a reputable landscaping company. At Vann Brothers Landscaping, we build relationships recognized for Quality, Integrity and Service. 

Our Vann Brothers Team members have been providing residential and commercial landscaping services to customers in Central Ontario for more than 25 years. We understand that there is no substitute for quality and professionalism.

Our mission is to provide our customers with the best possible value in every product and service we offer. We are dedicated to going beyond mere customer satisfaction.

We provide a full range of residential and commercial landscaping services including: Hardscapes, Softscapes, Outdoor patios, Decks, Gardens, Natural stone work, Natural stone walkways, Water features, Gazebos, Small excavation and driveways. 

Our skilled craftsmen are dedicated to delivering the best result for your home or commercial projects whether the project is small or large. High standards of quality, integrity and the commitment to total client satisfaction allow us to build a customer for life. 

“WE BUILD RELATIONSHIPS.” ​
